20230629 General
	Managed to build the csd0.img which is SYS: and found that BUILD
	has some problem with RKA0, RKB0, and DTA0 as seen in the CONNON
	handler.  When you try to insert them it cant find them even
	though the PRINT command shows them present.  I need to figure
	this out or some way to work around it.  I will probably try
	changing the names to RKA:, RKB:, and DTA:since I was not going
	to map more than one image anyway.

